        <h2>Each pair catches light differently.</h2>
        <p>Canary Pro's faceplate layers natural pearl with synthesized material, cut and placed by hand. The surface shifts from deep blue through green, gold, and violet as it moves. It is precise enough to read as engineered, but the pattern never repeats.</p>
