        <p class="cp-kicker">Canary Identity</p>
        <h2>Singapore color, built for the world.</h2>
        <p>The Canary Pro artwork carries AAW's Singapore origin: Merlion, skyline, orchid, tropical water, and canary motifs frame the monitor like a provenance mark. It places Canary Pro as a Singapore-built flagship, designed to move from local listening rooms to stages and meetups worldwide.</p>
