  <section class="cp-section cp-section--dark cp-specs">
    <div class="cp-wrap cp-specs__grid">
      <div>
        <p class="cp-kicker">Specifications</p>
        <h2>Fast, dense, extended.</h2>
        <p>Canary Pro is tuned for a vivid, high-contrast presentation: sub-bass control from the isobaric woofer pair, midrange clarity from the balanced armatures, and airy extension from the electrostatic quad.</p>
      </div>
      <dl class="cp-spec-table">
        <div><dt>Driver count</dt><dd>14 tri-hybrid drivers</dd></div>
